products.name: Gerber Cereal for Baby 2nd Foods Multigrain Cereal

extendedInfo.detail: Sitter.  11 grams of whole grains per serving. 60% DV of iron for learning-ability.  Non GMO Project verified. nongmoproject.org.  No. 1 pediatricians recommended brand (Among pediatricians who recommend infant cereal). 2nd Foods. Grain & Grow brings the goodness of whole grains and tailored nutrition. Iron to support brain development & learning ability. Gerber combines high quality whole grain goodness with 12 essential nutrients. We take action to protect the planet - so Gerber babies will grow and thrive for generations to come. Sitter: Your baby may be ready for this cereal if they: Sit independently. Pick up and hold small objects in hands. Reach for food or spoon when hungry. Use upper lip to help clear food off of spoon. This package is sold by weight, not volume, and may not appear full due to settling of contents. Every bite counts! Learn more.  Visit Gerber.com to chat with a MyGerber Baby Expert 1-800-4-Gerber; 24/7. Visit Gerber.com/sustainability to learn more.
extendedInfo.ingredients: Whole Grain Wheat Flour, Whole Grain Oat Flour, Oat Flour, Pearled Barley Flour, Potassium Phosphate, Vitamins And Minerals: Calcium Carbonate, Vitamin C (Ascorbic Acid), Iron (Electrolytic), Vitamin E (Alpha Tocopheryl Acetate), Zinc Sulfate, Niacinamide, Vitamin B2 (Riboflavin), Vitamin B1 (Thiamine Mononitrate), Vitamin B6 (Pyridoxine Hydrochloride), Folic Acid, Vitamin B12.
extendedInfo.directions: Microwave: Easy-to-Mix Directions: 1. Pour desired amount of cereal in bowl. 2. Stir in liquid (breastmilk or infant formula) to desired consistency. Serve as is or warm in the microwave. Always test temperature before feeding. Discard any unfed cereal. Completely cooked and ready to serve. Just add liquid. Mix! Microwave Guidelines for Heating: Warm unheated liquid at medium (50% power) for 15-30 seconds. Mix heated liquid with cereal. Stir to even out temperature. Test temperature before feeding.  Store in a cool, dry place.  Twist cap off, remove seal & twist back on.  Use within 30 days after opening.
extendedInfo.warnings: Contains: wheat.Do not use if seal is damaged. Keep container dry. Keep package away from children.
